divs: Sighting DetailsI was driving home from work on the 60 freeway towards Moreno Valley in California. It was around 6:10pm and as I was driving everyone had to of noticed this green blue light in the sky. It was very very bright it stayed stationary for about 3 seconds then disappeared and reappeared for another 5 seconds then vanished into thin air.
Summary: I was driving home from work and witnessed a very bright blue green light in the sky disappear and reappear for about ten seconds.
